msgid "Local development and debugging"
msgstr "本地开发与调试"

msgid "Embedded local cluster"
msgstr "嵌入式本地集群"

msgid ""
"Streaming execution calls ``ray.init()`` when no Ray runtime is active. This "
"starts a local cluster whose lifetime follows the Python process. You can "
"also start Ray first and attach to it. Pre-initialize Ray in the application "
"when you need custom dashboard, metrics-export, address, or resource "
"settings; Klein for Ray will reuse the active runtime:"
msgstr "当没有活动的 Ray 运行时，流处理执行会调用 ``ray.init()``。这将启动一个生命周期与 Python 进程一致的本地集群。你也可以先启动 Ray，再连接到它。需要自定义仪表板、指标导出、地址或资源设置时，请在应用中预先初始化 Ray；Klein for Ray 会复用活动的运行时："

msgid ""
"Use ``ray stop --force`` after interrupted local integration tests if Ray "
"processes remain."
msgstr "如果中断的本地集成测试遗留了 Ray 进程，请运行 ``ray stop --force``。"

msgid "In-process debug mode"
msgstr "进程内调试模式"

msgid ""
"Set ``RAY_KLEIN_DEBUG=1`` to replace Ray actors with local Python objects "
"and dedicated event-loop threads. This is useful for IDE breakpoints in "
"streaming operators, but it does not validate serialization, placement, "
"resource scheduling, process isolation, or Ray failure recovery."
msgstr "设置 ``RAY_KLEIN_DEBUG=1``，可用本地 Python 对象和专用事件循环线程替代 Ray actor。这适合在 IDE 中为流处理算子设置断点，但无法验证序列化、放置、资源调度、进程隔离或 Ray 故障恢复。"

msgid ""
"Run the integration suite without debug mode before relying on a pipeline in "
"production."
msgstr "在生产环境依赖某条流水线前，请先在不启用调试模式的情况下运行集成测试套件。"

msgid "Logging"
msgstr "日志"

msgid ""
"Libraries should not configure application logging on import. Applications "
"can call ``ray.klein.configure_logging()`` explicitly. Set "
"``RAY_KLEIN_LOGGING_CONFIG`` to load a custom YAML configuration."
msgstr "库不应在导入时配置应用日志。应用可以显式调用 ``ray.klein.configure_logging()``。设置 ``RAY_KLEIN_LOGGING_CONFIG`` 可加载自定义 YAML 配置。"
